AVID Hotel Prototype - Americas Market Development

Gensler 2017-2019
Working with the development team at IHG, the US Prototype was created to respond to a growing traveling demographic.


brand

AVID Hotels is a mid-scale brand of hotels developed for IHG that champions everyday travel at a fair price. See Developer/Investor Site for more information.

As the brand gained traction, several additional packages were developed for amenities and features, such as porte-cocheres, indoor and outdoor pools.
